CREATE TABLE filmes (
    color text, 
    director_name text, 
    num_critic_for_reviews float, 
    duration float, 
    director_facebook_likes float, 
    actor_3_facebook_likes float, 
    actor_2_name text, 
    actor_1_facebook_likes float, 
    gross float, 
    genres text, 
    actor_1_name text, 
    movie_title text, 
    num_voted_users float, 
    cast_total_facebook_likes float, 
    actor_3_name text, 
    facenumber_in_poster float, 
    plot_keywords text, 
    movie_imdb_link text, 
    num_user_for_reviews float, 
    language text, 
    country text, 
    content_rating text, 
    budget float, 
    title_year float, 
    actor_2_facebook_likes float, 
    imdb_score float, 
    aspect_ratio float, 
    movie_facebook_likes float, 
PRIMARY KEY (movie_title, genres, director_name, actor_1_name)
);
